{"tid":1637741,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[攬炒]蘇斯克查：曼聯如果輸給利物浦，我將被解僱。新教練不會像我那樣支持這些球員。","createTime":"2019-10-08T05:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T18:54:14.000Z","uid":103207,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"9de59f81f39901f980f227e1b332ee26efcbad96","tid":1637741,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:33:25.000Z","msg":"蘇帥更衣室怒斥球員：我下台！你們都不好受<br />\n<br />\n  據英國媒體《太陽報》消息，曼聯近來表現糟糕，在輸給紐卡素的比賽後，蘇斯克查（Ole Solskj&aelig;r）也在更衣室內發了火，但是似乎並沒有什麼效果。<br />\n<br />\n  報導表示，蘇斯克查連續第二周在更衣室內批評曼聯球員的表現令人尷尬，<span style=\"color: red;\">蘇帥甚至用了『你們會讓我下台』這樣的字眼</span>。他也直接告知隊員們，國際比賽日後，<span style=\"color: red;\">曼聯如果輸給利物浦，那麼自己將被解僱</span>。蘇帥也警告曼聯隊員們，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果他下台，那麼所有球員都會有危險，因為新教練不會像他那樣支持這些球員</span>。<br />\n<br />\n  但風筒是火力全開了，曼聯球員們還是看不到任何計畫。蘇斯克查似乎也根本沒有扭轉乾坤的能力。《太陽報》稱，曼聯正在迅速的分崩離析，連樂觀的蘇斯克查都看到了結局。一切都不順利，曼聯甚至可能不得不面對護級大戰，事情就是這麼糟糕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65404acdee58d530f9291d6ce9a31908bcf0147","tid":1637741,"uid":85911,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:36:48.000Z","msg":"太陽報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b99bcde7bd3cf945c981a6fd7fcc5c0dc7bc1c","tid":1637741,"uid":21969,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:45:54.000Z","msg":"痢狗又要玩爛件玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aef41f6ffbe90d452b20f291731f526dfeaad60","tid":1637741,"uid":50882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:58:50.000Z","msg":"成日都留比利執雞"},{"pid":"f8be1ef03c73a6614faee1a8c78a12865b0ffec8","tid":1637741,"uid":60177,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b65404acdee58d530f9291d6ce9a31908bcf0147","tid":1637741,"uid":85911,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T05:36:48.000Z","msg":"太陽報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:02:59.000Z","msg":"呢啲鳩噏野反而幾準<br />\n轉會野就信唔過"},{"pid":"7431c365f83a6255ffe9239a1d737ff858401985","tid":1637741,"uid":45518,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:07:00.000Z","msg":"班高層竟然覺得對猁有機唔使輸"},{"pid":"d373c64463cbcdc14952b8a2383044ec0f5b0c2a","tid":1637741,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:07:05.000Z","msg":"Ole Stay!"},{"pid":"2bf628aed0e5c8bf54dbdfd3682d90c32b8b6170","tid":1637741,"uid":53463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:53:07.000Z","msg":"又警告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4c00cc22150c09699159b34da1a2c36379f53d","tid":1637741,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:02:21.000Z","msg":"新教練不支持連加特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa1bf17bb63c1ca7c103afd19a56702513e2e52","tid":1637741,"uid":151324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:24:11.000Z","msg":"死利狗仲要迫走幾多個教練"},{"pid":"c1e87e960daa35ef43de34a2c2f192204914adf9","tid":1637741,"uid":60695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:36:02.000Z","msg":"除咗「這些球員」之外，開冬窗之前新教頭都冇其他球員可以畀佢支持喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa373c2bdd5bdcd00f69aeb0769fc044f819139","tid":1637741,"uid":61660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:37:03.000Z","msg":"高普同我醒醒定定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其餘十八隊睇緊你識唔識做"},{"pid":"5ceeaaab51956c06bc37ed9672c7d6ca9e2c1f86","tid":1637741,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:39:13.000Z","msg":"護級大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c